videos.headline: Maryland gets on board with 98-yard return TD
videos.description: Ty Johnson takes a kickoff back 98 yards as Maryland takes the lead over Michigan.

videos.headline: Michigan RB powers in for TD
videos.description: Michigan's Ben Mason powers through for a one-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Shea Patterson finds WR for a 51-yard gain
videos.description: Michigan's Shea Patterson threads the needle as he finds Nico Collins for a 51-yard gain.

videos.headline: Shea Patterson throws across body for 22-yard TD
videos.description: Michigan's Shea Patterson takes a big shot as he finds Ronnie Bell for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Michigan RB hurdles defender
videos.description: Michigan's Ben Mason makes a spectacular play as he hurdles defender for a 15-yard gain.

videos.headline: Maryland LB Lewis ejected for targeting
videos.description: Maryland's Rayshad Lewis gets ejected in the third quarter for targeting.

videos.headline: 2nd Maryland player is ejected for targeting
videos.description: Maryland's Tre Watson gets ejected for targeting after a hit on Donovan Peoples-Jones.

videos.headline: Michigan RB escapes for 28-yard gain
videos.description: Michigan's Tru Wilson jukes defenders for a 28-yard gain.

videos.headline: Patterson throws 3rd TD pass for Michigan
videos.description: Shea Patterson finds Jared Wangler for a 7-yard touchdown as Michigan extends its lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Michigan takes back INT for 46-yard TD
videos.description: Brandon Watson picks off Kasim Hill and returns it 46 yards for a Michigan touchdown.
